  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to your wishlist now to get notified on release!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/547e136fd5caeaa4c2c1d265a83d50ab.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Software</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/b13d5f48e1c1782b5e6f2e50d65d0538.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/b13d5f48e1c1782b5e6f2e50d65d0538.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/b13d5f48e1c1782b5e6f2e50d65d0538.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Drawing hands and feet is one of the biggest challenges in art. With HAELE 3D – Hand Poses Pro, you'll always have the perfect hand reference at your fingertips. It includes a wide range of built-in poses and preset scenes, but if you need something specific, you can easily create your own custom hand poses—whether it's one or two hands, with props or objects. Choose between male and female models, adjust materials, morphs, skin tones, and textures, and fine-tune the environment and lighting to craft the perfect reference for your needs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/83c8d610767cdaef8dfb99e1dd320faa.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/83c8d610767cdaef8dfb99e1dd320faa.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/83c8d610767cdaef8dfb99e1dd320faa.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/74f5706a2d7ba72188a036f4b2639452.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/74f5706a2d7ba72188a036f4b2639452.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/74f5706a2d7ba72188a036f4b2639452.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/8dd643df60e28152f1b086779fe1bacc.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/8dd643df60e28152f1b086779fe1bacc.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/8dd643df60e28152f1b086779fe1bacc.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Female and male hands with morph targets<br></li><li> Various, highly realistic skin tone textures<br></li><li> Props (Weapons, Glasses, Food, and many more various items)<br></li><li> Editable preset poses<br></li><li> Editable lights and environments<br></li><li> Custom backgrounds<br></li><li> Adjustable camera angle, location, position and field of view<br></li><li> Save and load scenes</li></ul><br>HAELE 3D - Hand Poses Pro is an easy to use anatomy and gesture drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. With a diverse range of editable options, it serves as a resource for learning how to draw human hands. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between, this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your hand drawing, painting or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/b13d5f48e1c1782b5e6f2e50d65d0538.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/b13d5f48e1c1782b5e6f2e50d65d0538.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/b13d5f48e1c1782b5e6f2e50d65d0538.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Drawing hands and feet is one of the biggest challenges in art. With HAELE 3D – Hand Poses Pro, you'll always have the perfect hand reference at your fingertips. It includes a wide range of built-in poses and preset scenes, but if you need something specific, you can easily create your own custom hand poses—whether it's one or two hands, with props or objects. Choose between male and female models, adjust materials, morphs, skin tones, and textures, and fine-tune the environment and lighting to craft the perfect reference for your needs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/83c8d610767cdaef8dfb99e1dd320faa.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/83c8d610767cdaef8dfb99e1dd320faa.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/83c8d610767cdaef8dfb99e1dd320faa.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/74f5706a2d7ba72188a036f4b2639452.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/74f5706a2d7ba72188a036f4b2639452.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/74f5706a2d7ba72188a036f4b2639452.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/8dd643df60e28152f1b086779fe1bacc.poster.avif?t=1773168316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/8dd643df60e28152f1b086779fe1bacc.webm?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540240/extras/8dd643df60e28152f1b086779fe1bacc.mp4?t=1773168316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Female and male hands with morph targets<br></li><li> Various, highly realistic skin tone textures<br></li><li> Props (Weapons, Glasses, Food, and many more various items)<br></li><li> Editable preset poses<br></li><li> Editable lights and environments<br></li><li> Custom backgrounds<br></li><li> Adjustable camera angle, location, position and field of view<br></li><li> Save and load scenes</li></ul><br>HAELE 3D - Hand Poses Pro is an easy to use anatomy and gesture drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. With a diverse range of editable options, it serves as a resource for learning how to draw human hands. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between, this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your hand drawing, painting or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.",
